\id HOS  
\h Hosea 
\mt1 Hosea  
\toc1 Hosea 
\toc2 Hosea  
\c 1  
\iex Prophetangka Hoseangka Israel-warranda yalaman, “Yurra Israel-warra bulmbuy bajaku. Yurrawundu buyun-buyundu yurranin jurrngal. Yurra wawu kari junkayku dunganka. Yinyaynka jana bamangka cheeky-balangka yurranin buyun-damal. Yurra Israel-warrangka bayan jirray ngaran, yamba yurra yurrawunku Godunku milka-wulan. Yinyaynka bamangka cheeky-balangka yurranin yalaymun bubumun wundil, slave-bungal. Yamba juma Israel-warra Godunduku jurrkiji baja. Jana yalarrku jurrkiji baja bamandaku Davidandamun.”  